How do you know him?

178
00:16:59,660 --> 00:17:01,051
他几年前曾来伦敦作演讲
Well, he came to London a few years ago

179
00:17:01,052 --> 00:17:02,448
谈论唯心论
to lecture on spiritualism.

180
