221
00:22:26,549 --> 00:22:28,503
布鲁斯卡不同 所以他才把
Brusca didn't. That's why he

222
00:22:28,504 --> 00:22:30,552
那些物件寄给你以作查证
sent the items to you for verification.

223
00:22:30,854 --> 00:22:34,255
