228
00:22:45,235 --> 00:22:48,864
包括一件新教时期的衣服
including a dress that may have been from pagan times.

229
00:22:50,874 --> 00:22:53,329
传说发现骨灰瓮的
As the legend has it, packs of wolves

230
00:22:53,330 --> 00:22:54,530
第二天晚上
came out of the forest...

231
00:22:54,565 --> 00:22:56,675
大批狼群从森林中奔涌而出
the night after the urn was found.

232
00:22:56,746 --> 00:22:59,943
他们把新埋入墓地的尸体挖出来
They dug up freshly-buried bodies in the graveyard...

233
00:23:00,016 --> 00:23:02,075
