你疯了吗? 他们能利用信号追踪你
Are you crazy? They can trace you with it.

533
00:52:01,043 --> 00:52:03,603
你说得对 扔了它
You're right. Fuck it.

534
00:52:07,650 --> 00:52:10,551
今晚来我家睡吧 安全一点
Come to my place tonight. It'll be safer for you.

535
00:52:10,620 --> 00:52:12,554
不 我想要回家
No, I'd rather go home.

536
00:52:12,622 --> 00:52:14,590
迈克尔可以去那儿找我
Michael can reach me there.

537
00:52:16,659 --> 00:52:19,287
这是我的电话号码和地址
Here's my phone number and address.

538
00:52:19,362 --> 00:52:22,388
任何时候打给我都可以      谢谢
Call me anytime. It's no bother.        Thank you.

539
00:52:22,465 --> 00:52:26,231
你是埃莉莎的女儿 这比家人还亲
You're Elisa's daughter. That's closer than family.

540
00:52:26,302 --> 00:52:29,897
我并不想吓唬你 但是...
I don't mean to scare you, but...

541
00:52:29,972 --> 00:52:31,906
他们知道你是谁 萨拉
they know who you are, Sarah.

542
00:52:31,974 --> 00:52:34,909
向我保证你不会相信任何人
Promise me you won't trust anyone.

543
00:52:34,977 --> 00:52:36,968
我保证
I promise.

544
00:52:43,319 --> 00:52:45,310
发生什么事了?
What's going on here?

545
00:52:45,388 --> 00:52:48,221
他们在焚烧教堂
They are burning the churches.

546
00:52:48,291 --> 00:52:50,282
情况越来越糟
It's getting worse.

547
00:53:13,883 --> 00:53:16,579
母亲! 母亲!
Mater! Mater!

548
00:55:01,157 --> 00:55:03,352
我的公寓里有人!
There was somebody at my apartment.!

549
00:55:03,426 --> 00:55:05,253
我从门缝中看到了灯光还有影子
I saw lights and shadows under the door.

550
00:55:05,254 --> 00:55:07,055
我觉得我要疯了
I feel like I'm going crazy!

551
00:55:07,163 --> 00:55:11,224
天哪! 救我 请救救我! 请救救我!
God! Help. Please help me. Help me, please.

552
00:55:11,300 --> 00:55:13,291
深呼吸
Take a deep breath.

553
00:55:18,507 --> 00:55:21,442
谢谢你      冷静下来
Thank you.        Calm down.

554
00:55:21,510 --> 00:55:23,501
进来
Come in.

555
00:55:25,715 --> 00:55:28,149
埃尔加 这是萨拉      你好
Elga, meet Sarah.        Hi.

556
00:55:28,217 --> 00:55:30,549
她在这里做什么?      没事的
What is she doing here?        It's okay.

557
00:55:30,620 --> 00:55:32,281
玛塔 你必须帮帮我
Marta, you have to help me.

558
00:55:32,282 --> 00:55:33,514
我不知道自己出什么事了
I don't know what's happening to me.

559
00:55:33,623 --> 00:55:36,251
跟我来      你必须向我解释
Come with me.        You have to explain.

560
00:55:36,325 --> 00:55:38,259
为什么有这么多事发生在我身上 为什么?
Why is all this happening to me? Why?

561
00:55:38,327 --> 00:55:41,262
他们知道你是谁 他们不会冒险的
They know who you are. They can't take any chances.

562
00:55:41,330 --> 00:55:44,561
但我 我 我什么都不知道
But I- I- I don't know anything.

563
00:55:44,634 --> 00:55:47,569
你比自己想象的知道更多
You know more than you think you do.

564
00:55:47,637 --> 00:55:49,184
不然有这么多怪物追逐你
How else have you survived this long

565
00:55:49,185 --> 00:55:50,885
你如何能活到现在?
with those monsters after you?

566
00:55:57,613 --> 00:56:00,548
埃尔加 能让我们单独呆会儿吗?
Elga, would you please excuse us for a minute?

567
00:56:00,616 --> 00:56:02,550
拜托 求你了
Oh, please. Come on.

568
00:56:02,618 --> 00:56:04,609
拜托?
Please?

569
00:56:10,426 --> 00:56:13,122
你有天赋 萨拉
You have gifts, Sarah.

570
00:56:13,195 --> 00:56:16,528
如果你想活下去 就必须接受现实
You need to accept that if you want to survive.

571
00:56:42,692 --> 00:56:45,388
好好看
Watch and learn.

572
00:57:02,478 --> 00:57:04,639
飘荡的灵魂
Drifting spirits.

573
00:57:05,848 --> 00:57:09,306
他们无处不在 罗马尤其多
They are everywhere, especially here in Rome.

574
00:57:11,754 --> 00:57:14,245
老房子里到处都是鬼魂
The old houses are full of ghosts.

575
00:57:14,323 --> 00:57:16,257
想一想
Think about it.

576
00:57:16,325 --> 00:57:19,351
罗马城有2700年的历史...
The city is 27 00 years old...

577
00:57:19,428 --> 00:57:23,364
我们正站在五层坟墓之上
and we are standing on five layers of graves.

578
00:57:23,432 --> 00:57:26,526
你怎么做的?      你也可以做到
How do you do it?        You can do it too.

579
00:57:26,602 --> 00:57:29,901
运用你的天赋 就可以见人所未见
With your gifts, you can see what others can't.

580
00:57:36,212 --> 00:57:38,373
闭上眼睛
Close your eyes.

581
00:57:41,016 --> 00:57:43,917
聚集你所有能量...
Focus all of your energy...

582
00:57:43,986 --> 00:57:47,251
集中在这一点上
and concentrate on this spot.

583
00:57:48,924 --> 00:57:51,017
很好
Good.

584
00:57:52,461 --> 00:57:55,760
现在像我做的那样 轻吹一口气
Now just do like I did and blow.

585
00:58:19,522 --> 00:58:21,581
萨拉
Sarah.

586
00:58:21,657 --> 00:58:23,648
不 不可能啊
No, it can't be.

587
00:58:24,960 --> 00:58:26,951
妈咪?
Mommy?

588
00:58:27,029 --> 00:58:29,429
萨拉
Sarah.

589
00:58:29,498 --> 00:58:32,433
妈咪!      不要碰她 不然她会消失的
Mommy!        You can't touch her or she'll disappear.

590
00:58:32,501 --> 00:58:34,401
别管我
Leave me alone.

591
00:58:34,470 --> 00:58:39,271
泪之母越来越强大 越来越强 萨拉!
Mater Lacrimarum grows stronger. She grows stronger, Sarah!

592
00:58:39,341 --> 00:58:41,241
你在哪儿啊?
Where-Where are you?

593
00:58:41,310 --> 00:58:44,074
妈咪! 妈咪!
Mommy! Mommy!

594
00:58:44,146 --> 00:58:47,138
你的处境很危险 亲爱的孩子
You're in great danger, my dear child.

595
00:58:47,216 --> 00:58:49,514
学会战斗      不要!
Learn to fight.        No.!

596
00:58:49,585 --> 00:58:51,177
不要! 不要!
No! No!

597
00:58:51,253 --> 00:58:55,246
别走 妈咪! 请不要离开我 妈咪 求你!
Don't go, Mommy.! Don't leave me.! Mommy, please.!

598
00:58:55,324 --> 00:58:57,792
妈咪!
Mommy!

599
00:58:57,860 --> 00:59:00,158
请把她带回来 求你!
Please make her come back. Please!

600
00:59:00,229 --> 00:59:02,026
妈...
Mo-

601
00:59:02,097 --> 00:59:04,793
不要离开我 不要走
Don't leave me. Don't leave.

602
00:59:12,408 --> 00:59:14,740
她让我战斗
She told me to fight.

603
00:59:14,810 --> 00:59:18,678
你一定要帮助我 我必须战斗 求你
You have to help me. I have to fight. Please.

604
00:59:20,182 --> 00:59:22,946
我只是个巫女
I'm only a psychic.

605
00:59:23,018 --> 00:59:28,183
我能与灵魂交流 仅此而已
I can communicate with spirits, but that's about it.

606
00:59:29,692 --> 00:59:32,957
我没有你母亲的天赋 也没有你的
I don't have your mother's gifts, or yours.

607
00:59:35,030 --> 00:59:37,187
你需要人指引你
You need someone who can guide you,

608
00:59:37,188 --> 00:59:39,107
为你指出正确的方向
point you in the right direction.

609
00:59:39,142 --> 00:59:41,332
是的
Yes.

610
00:59:41,403 --> 00:59:44,634
明天我会把你介绍给古格列尔莫・德威特
Tomorrow I'll introduce you to Guglielmo de Witt.

611
00:59:44,707 --> 00:59:47,574
他是个伟大的比利时思想家      好的
He's a great Belgian thinker.        Okay.

612
00:59:47,643 --> 00:59:52,080
他会告诉你些有用的信息 但愿不会太迟
He'll tell you something useful, if it's not too late.

613
00:59:55,417 --> 00:59:58,045
谢谢你
Thank you.

614
00:59:58,120 --> 01:00:01,248
谢谢你
Thank you.

615
01:00:11,934 --> 01:00:14,562
不 不
No. No.

616
01:02:12,384 --> 01:02:14,614
快接电话
Pick up the phone.

617
01:02:14,686 --> 01:02:17,814
快点 玛塔 快接电话!
Come on, Marta, pick up the phone!

618
01:02:28,967 --> 01:02:31,333
喂? 喂 玛塔?
Hello? Hello, Marta?

619
01:02:31,403 --> 01:02:33,431
玛塔 你必须马上离开那里
Marta, you have to get out of there now!

620
01:02:33,500 --> 01:02:36,156
玛塔? 喂? 谁在听?
Marta? Hello? Who's there?

621
01:02:36,642 --> 01:02:39,338
快跑! 太晚了!
Run! It's too late!

622
01:02:39,411 --> 01:02:41,276
现在! 快跑!
Now! Run now!

623
01:03:06,338 --> 01:03:08,602
不! 她什么都不知道!
No.! She doesn't know anything.!

624
01:03:08,674 --> 01:03:10,869
不! 不要啊! 不要!
No! Don't do it! Don't do it!

625
01:04:14,898 --> 01:04:17,264
母亲! 母亲!
Mater! Mater!

626
01:04:17,334 --> 01:04:19,632
萨拉在哪儿?
Where is Sarah?

627
01:04:19,703 --> 01:04:21,762
她不在这儿
She isn't here.

628
01:04:21,839 --> 01:04:23,864
笨蛋!
Idiot!

629
01:04:30,381 --> 01:04:33,646
是你
It is you.

630
01:04:33,717 --> 01:04:36,686
是的
It is.

631
01:05:07,479 --> 01:05:10,414
别倒下 别倒下!
Stay strong. Stay strong.!

632
01:05:10,482 --> 01:05:13,178
妈妈      别倒下 萨拉!
Mom.        Stay strong, Sarah!

633
01:05:13,252 --> 01:05:16,085
好的
Yes.

634
01:05:18,924 --> 01:05:22,360
妈妈 他们对你和爸爸做了什么...
Mom, what did they do to you and Dad when-

635
01:05:22,428 --> 01:05:24,623
事情已经过去了
It's all in the past.

636
01:05:24,697 --> 01:05:27,723
你什么也改变不了 注定要这样的
There's nothing you can do. It was meant to be.

637
01:05:27,800 --> 01:05:31,167
你离开我时 我是那么沮丧 那么生气
I was so upset, so angry at you for leaving me.

638
01:05:31,236 --> 01:05:33,170
请你不要再次抛弃我
Plea- Please don't abandon me again.

639
01:05:33,238 --> 01:05:35,866
原谅我 小萨拉
Forgive me, little Sarah.

640
01:05:35,941 --> 01:05:38,535
我不能再说了
I can't speak anymore.

641
01:05:38,610 --> 01:05:41,579
我现在属于另一个地方 使用你的天赋
I belong to another place now. Use your gifts.

642
01:05:41,647 --> 01:05:44,047
使用它们 使用它们
Use them. Use them.

643
01:05:44,116 --> 01:05:46,107
妈咪
Mommy.

644
01:05:48,187 --> 01:05:49,363
好的 伙计们 听好了
Okay, guys, listen up.

645
01:05:49,364 --> 01:05:51,663
我们要找一个约28岁的女孩
We're looking for a girl around 28.

646
01:05:52,024 --> 01:05:53,666
她的名字叫萨拉・曼蒂
Her name is Sarah Mandy.

647
01:05:53,667 --> 01:05:55,926
如果你看到了 不要接近她
If you see her, don't approach her.

648
01:06:00,799 --> 01:06:02,767
迈克尔?
Michael?

649
01:06:02,835 --> 01:06:05,429
迈克尔 迈...
Michael. Mi-

650
01:06:06,438 --> 01:06:09,601
迈克尔! 迈克尔!
Michael! Michael!

651
01:06:12,478 --> 01:06:14,469
迈克尔 停下!
Michael, stop!

652
01:06:15,848 --> 01:06:17,543
迈克尔?
Michael?

653
01:06:20,486 --> 01:06:22,784
迈克尔
Michael.

654
01:06:22,855 --> 01:06:25,085
你没事吧?
Are you okay?

655
01:06:25,157 --> 01:06:27,091
迈克尔 你生病了
Michael, you're sick.

656
01:06:27,159 --> 01:06:29,787
保罗在哪儿?
Where's Paul?

657
01:06:29,862 --> 01:06:31,796
我还以为...
I thought-

658
01:06:31,864 --> 01:06:33,798
你有没有...
Did you-

659
01:06:33,866 --> 01:06:35,959
我想...
I think-

660
01:06:36,034 --> 01:06:40,368
我想他... 我想他死了
I think he's- I think he's dead.

661
01:06:40,439 --> 01:06:43,067
我的天哪      他们杀了他
Oh, my God.        They killed him.

662
01:06:43,142 --> 01:06:45,076
我的天哪      而我却不能...
Oh, my God.        And I can't-

663
01:06:45,144 --> 01:06:48,307
我现在不想说这件事
I don't want to talk about that now.

664
01:06:49,848 --> 01:06:51,782
我们走吧
Let's go.

665
01:06:51,850 --> 01:06:53,784
我的公寓不安全
My apartment is not safe.

666
01:06:53,852 --> 01:06:54,775
不管我走到哪里 他们...
Everywhere I go, they-

667
01:06:54,800 --> 01:06:56,139
我们去我家
We'll go to my place.

668
01:06:56,855 --> 01:06:59,119
他们不会上那儿找你
They won't look for you there.

669
01:07:04,196 --> 01:07:06,187
不 不 不要开灯
No, no. No lights.

670
01:07:06,265 --> 01:07:08,199
为什么?
Why?

671
01:07:08,267 --> 01:07:10,667
你不想被他们看到吧
We don't want them to see us.

672
01:07:13,839 --> 01:07:16,831
我真高兴 我们找到了彼此
I'm so happy we found each other.

673
01:07:18,677 --> 01:07:21,111
你没事吧?
Are you okay?

674
01:07:21,180 --> 01:07:23,259
你要不休息一下 把外套脱了
Why don't you just rest, take off your coat-

675
01:07:23,260 --> 01:07:24,127
不 不 不
No, no, no.

676
01:07:25,684 --> 01:07:27,618
我太冷了 对不起 我太冷了
I'm freezing. Sorry. I'm freezing.

677
01:07:27,686 --> 01:07:30,621
我连一晚都没有在房子里呆过
I just haven't spent a- a single night inside.

678
01:07:30,689 --> 01:07:31,992
我把每个地方都找遍了
I looked everywhere for him.

679
01:07:31,993 --> 01:07:33,201
发生什么事了?
Yeah, what happened?

680
01:07:33,236 --> 01:07:34,067
因为我去蒙特里尼
Because I went to Monteleone

681
01:07:34,068 --> 01:07:35,307
找你了      我没去成
to find you.        I couldn't get there.

682
01:07:37,830 --> 01:07:40,390
他们在跟踪我
They were following me.

683
01:07:40,465 --> 01:07:44,697
你想告诉我的所有事 我现在都明白了
Everything you were trying to tell me I understand now.

684
01:07:44,770 --> 01:07:46,931
对不起 我以前不相信你
I'm sorry I didn't believe you.

685
01:07:47,005 --> 01:07:48,870
真的很抱歉
I'm really sorry.

686
01:07:48,941 --> 01:07:50,932
好吧
Okay.

687
01:07:52,010 --> 01:07:54,604
你可能不该吸烟
Maybe you shouldn't smoke.

688
01:07:54,680 --> 01:07:56,773
你为什么不...
Why don't you-

689
01:07:56,849 --> 01:08:00,341
你想要我做点什么吗? 喝点茶怎么样?
Do you want me to fix something? Tea, maybe?

690
01:08:00,419 --> 01:08:02,410
不要
No.

691
01:08:04,790 --> 01:08:07,224
不 我... 我没事
No, I'm f- I'm fine.

692
01:08:07,292 --> 01:08:10,318
我只是
I'm just-

693
01:08:10,395 --> 01:08:13,694
我只是太开心了 又找到你了
I'm just pleased I found you again.

694
01:08:13,765 --> 01:08:16,598
我没事 别担心 没事的
I'm fine. Don't worry. Fine.

695
01:08:22,641 --> 01:08:25,166
迈克尔 你在流血!
Michael,you're bleeding.!

696
01:08:30,883 --> 01:08:34,216
没事的      迈克尔 你受伤了!
It's nothing.        Michael,you're hurt.!

697
01:08:34,286 --> 01:08:36,345
不 没关系的
No, it's- it's okay.

698
01:08:36,421 --> 01:08:38,514
没事的
It's nothing.

699
01:08:38,590 --> 01:08:41,024
你说什么 没事? 你受伤了!
What do you mean, it's nothing? You're hurt!

700
01:08:41,093 --> 01:08:43,527
跟你说了没事! 走开!
I told you it's nothing! Get off me!

701
01:08:43,595 --> 01:08:47,031
我说了 滚开!
I told you to get the fuck off me!

702
01:08:56,842 --> 01:09:02,178
你以为他们会放过 我和我的孩子吗?
Do you think they would spare me and my child?

703
01:09:02,247 --> 01:09:05,444
你太天真了
You're so naive.

704
01:09:05,517 --> 01:09:07,451
你逃不掉的
You can't escape her.

705
01:09:07,519 --> 01:09:09,248
但他们杀了你的儿子!
But they killed your son!

706
01:09:09,321 --> 01:09:13,951
你的母亲再也不能帮你了
Your mother can't help you anymore.

707
01:09:14,026 --> 01:09:17,120
我们现在拥有同一个母亲
We all have one mother now.

708
01:09:17,195 --> 01:09:20,596
泪之母
The Mother of Tears.

709
01:09:22,634 --> 01:09:25,797
你这个笨蛋...
You bitch! Oh, you crazy-

710
01:09:26,505 --> 01:09:28,973
你这个疯婆子
you crazy bitch.!

711
01:09:57,569 --> 01:10:01,198
古格里尔莫 玛塔给你的那个名字
Guglielmo. The name Marta gave you.

712
01:10:01,273 --> 01:10:03,264
去找他
Find him.

713
01:10:14,786 --> 01:10:17,687
妈咪!
Mommy!

714
01:10:17,756 --> 01:10:19,656
萨拉!
Sarah!

715
01:11:00,832 --> 01:11:03,767
