Welcome back to the morning news.

716
01:11:03,835 --> 01:11:05,769
现在是今日焦点
And now for today's top story.

717
01:11:05,837 --> 01:11:07,388
他们称其为 罗马的再次沦陷
They're calling it the second fall of Rome.

718
01:11:07,500 --> 01:11:09,422
过去几天以来 罗马城
Over the past few days the city has

719
01:11:09,423 --> 01:11:11,235
