As you can see, I- I'm not very mobile.

748
01:13:43,595 --> 01:13:47,087
我来这里是因为我要问你...
I'm here because I- I have to ask you about-

749
01:13:55,774 --> 01:14:00,711
我们炼金术士确实修习古老的艺术...
We alchemists may practice an ancient art...

750
01:14:00,779 --> 01:14:03,612
但我们也看新闻
but we do watch the news.

751
01:14:03,682 --> 01:14:07,516
你以为我会不知道你是谁吗 萨拉・曼蒂?
Do you think I wouldn't know who you are, Sarah Mandy?

752
01:14:07,586 --> 01:14:09,176
警察正到处找你
And that the police is looking for you

753
