Well, it's good too.

758
01:14:30,108 --> 01:14:32,133
我们研究巫术 科学...
Some of what we do is magic, science...

759
01:14:32,210 --> 01:14:35,907
神秘学 神智学 自然法则
esoterism, theosophy, natural law.

760
01:14:35,981 --> 01:14:40,077
