Marta Colussi sent you, I see.

767
01:15:14,319 --> 01:15:17,584
还有你母亲 埃莉莎・曼蒂
So did your mother, Elisa Mandy.

768
01:15:28,867 --> 01:15:31,233
你对我做了什么?
What did you do to me?

769
01:15:31,303 --> 01:15:34,701
你以为我连你是谁都不弄清楚
Did you expect me to just let you waltz in here

770
01:15:34,702 --> 01:15:38,072
