people like my mother.

782
01:16:20,251 --> 01:16:23,152
约翰内斯神父说...
Father Johannes said that-

783
01:16:23,221 --> 01:16:25,148
眼泪之母将带来
that Mater Lacrimarum is bringing

784
01:16:25,149 --> 01:16:27,220
第二个女巫时代
on the Second Age of Witches.

785
01:16:27,255 --> 01:16:30,156
