Somewhere in the city the celebration has already begun.

787
01:16:34,632 --> 01:16:36,656
但恐怕没有什么白女巫
But I'm afraid there is no army of good witches

788
01:16:36,657 --> 01:16:38,546
可以拯救这座城市
out there to come to the rescue.

789
01:16:39,104 --> 01:16:42,699
如果你想要制止她 就必须独自行动
If you want to stop her, you have to do it yourself.

790
01:16:42,774 --> 01:16:45,038
那么我现在是独自一人?
So I'm on my own now?

791
01:16:45,110 --> 01:16:47,044
我又没说不帮忙
I didn't say I wouldn't help.

792
01:16:47,112 --> 01:16:50,878
我不能给你答案 但我可以提供信息
I can't give you answers, but I can share information.

793
01:16:50,949 --> 01:16:53,383
跟我来
Follow me.

794
