几个世纪前 有个叫做维拉里的
Centuries ago, a great Roman

795
01:16:55,738 --> 01:16:57,688
伟大的罗马炼金术士...
alchemist named Varelli...

796
01:16:58,690 --> 01:17:01,750
在这所房子住过一段时间
lived for a time in this villa.

797
01:17:01,826 --> 01:17:04,852
他还是个有才华的建筑师
He was also a gifted architect.

798
01:17:04,929 --> 01:17:06,674
在他生命结束之时
And near the end of his life,

799
01:17:06,900 --> 01:17:09,735
他为那三位母亲建造了住所
he built the residences for the Three Mothers.

800
01:17:23,214 --> 01:17:26,240
这或许能为你提供一点信息
This may tell you something you need to know.

801
01:17:46,471 --> 01:17:49,235
三位母亲
The Three Mothers.

802
01:17:51,242 --> 01:17:54,268
我不知道我要付出怎样的代价...
I don't know how much it will cost me...

803
01:17:54,345 --> 01:17:58,975
因打破炼金术士所称作的"沉默"
to break what we alchemists have always called SI LENTI UM.

804
01:18:03,755 --> 01:18:05,689
我见到了那三位母亲...
I met the three Mothers...

805
01:18:05,757 --> 01:18:07,816
为他们建造了三所房子
and built three houses for them:

806
01:18:07,892 --> 01:18:10,986
一所位于弗莱堡 一所位于纽约...
one in Freiburg, one in New York...

807
01:18:11,062 --> 01:18:13,724
一所位于罗马
and one in Rome.

808
01:18:13,798 --> 01:18:15,851
我发现这些房子里
I discovered too late that

809
01:18:15,852 --> 01:18:18,595
藏有肮脏的秘密时 已经太迟了
these houses hide obscene secrets.

810
01:18:18,903 --> 01:18:22,498
那些姐妹就是从这里...
It is from here that the sisters spread pain...

811
01:18:22,574 --> 01:18:25,805
向全世界散播苦难 泪水和黑暗
tears and darkness throughout the world.

812
01:18:33,318 --> 01:18:37,186
这应该是维拉里在罗马建造的那所房子
This building should be the one Varelli built in Rome.

