是个谜语
It's a riddle.

817
01:18:50,935 --> 01:18:53,733
找到眼泪之母的住所...
Find where Mater Lacrimarum resides...

818
01:18:53,805 --> 01:18:55,898
你就找到了谜底
and you'll find the answer.

819
01:18:55,974 --> 01:18:58,568
你真的要这么做?
Are you sure you want to do this?

820
01:19:00,011 --> 01:19:02,639
我还有选择吗?
Do I have a choice?

821
01:20:01,639 --> 01:20:05,632
母亲
Mater.

822
01:20:05,710 --> 01:20:07,644
母亲
Mater.

823
01:20:07,712 --> 01:20:10,044
母亲
Mater.

824
01:20:10,114 --> 01:20:12,480
母亲
Mater.

825
01:20:17,088 --> 01:20:19,283
停车 就停在这里!
Stop. Stop right here!

826
01:24:20,631 --> 01:24:23,327
嗨! 你是谁?
Hey! Who are you?

827
01:24:23,401 --> 01:24:26,393
我 我刚看见几个女人走进来
I, uh- I just saw some women come in.

828
01:24:26,470 --> 01:24:28,404
你看到她们了吗?      没有
Did you see them?        No.

829
01:24:28,472 --> 01:24:31,373
