A long time.

833
01:24:38,916 --> 01:24:41,646
三四十年了
Thirty, forty years.

834
01:24:41,719 --> 01:24:47,214
从纳粹在二战末逃走开始
Since the Nazis escaped at the end of the war.

835
01:24:47,291 --> 01:24:50,556
你来之前 谁住在这里?
And who used to live here before you?

836
01:24:50,628 --> 01:24:54,359
我不知道 某个协会
Oh, I don't know. A kind of association.

837
01:24:54,432 --> 01:24:58,163
哲学家 抑或是艺术家 不记得了
Philosophers. Artists maybe. I don't remember.

838
01:24:58,236 --> 01:25:00,227
