Those are the same symbols I saw on the urn.

859
01:27:58,682 --> 01:28:01,048
地下墓穴
Catacombs.

860
01:28:01,118 --> 01:28:03,746
这些是未发掘的地下墓穴
These are unexplored catacombs.

861
