01:37:10,134 --> 01:37:12,125
萨拉!
Sarah.!

903
01:37:12,202 --> 01:37:15,638
嘘 嘘 是我! 是我! 是我! 是我!
Shh! Shh! It's me, it's me! It's me! It's me!

904
01:37:15,706 --> 01:37:19,574
